# Backend base URL (no trailing slash).
#
# Recommended for local development: leave unset or empty so requests use the same origin as the Vite dev
# server and the `/api` proxy (see vite.config.js) forwards to the API on port 3000. Session cookies then
# stay on http://localhost:5173.
#
# If you set a full URL (e.g. http://localhost:3000), the browser calls the API cross-origin; you must set
# backend CORS_ORIGIN to include the frontend origin (e.g. http://localhost:5173) and use credentials.
# VITE_API_URL=
